<arggraph id="micro_c185" topic_id="sports_as_family_activity" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Families participating in sports teams can be a good way to bond.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[When families are competing together and working together as a team they feel more connected and engaged with each other.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[It is also an excellent way to improve the family's total health.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Sports also helps to teach families discipline.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[The risk of injury is a possible side effect from families doing sports together,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[but the positive benefits far outweigh any risks.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7" implicit="true"><![CDATA[Doing sports together is a good thing for families.]]></edu>
